---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Christen Thompson for Heber City Council</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Campaign website for Christen Thompson, Heber City Council."
    />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen font-sans">
    <header class="bg-green-900 text-white py-6 shadow">
      <div
        class="container mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between px-4"
      >
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">
          <a href="/" class="hover:underline"
            >Christen Thompson for Heber City Council</a
          >
        </h1>
        <nav class="mt-4 md:mt-0">
          <a href="/" class="mr-6 hover:underline">Home</a>
          <a href="/about" class="mr-6 hover:underline">About</a>
          <a href="/blog" class="mr-6 hover:underline">Blog</a>
          <a href="/donate" class="hover:underline">Donate</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-10">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Open Space -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 flex flex-col items-center">
          <img
            src="/images/Heber Valley Rays.jpg"
            alt="Open Space"
            class="rounded mb-4 w-full h-40 object-cover"
          />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Open Space</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
            Protect Heber Valley from urban sprawl through conservation
            easements, zoning that matches our general plan to preserve the
            majority of land as open space with public access and follow
            Midway's example. Put an open space bond on the ballot and preserve
            what we can for future generations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Clean Water -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 flex flex-col items-center">
          <img
            src="/images/ValleyView.png"
            alt="Clean Water"
            class="rounded mb-4 w-full h-40 object-cover"
          />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Clean Water</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
            Expand our sensitive lands ordinance to protect more drainage areas
            and Heber Valley's water supply.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Clean Air -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 flex flex-col items-center">
          <img
            src="/images/DeerSunrise.png"
            alt="Clean Air"
            class="rounded mb-4 w-full h-40 object-cover"
          />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Clean Air</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
            Work with the county to expand transit. We need a bus going from
            Provo Airport, through Heber, directly to the Salt Lake City Airport
            and the reverse.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Affordability -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 flex flex-col items-center">
          <img
            src="/images/Timp.jpg"
            alt="Affordability"
            class="rounded mb-4 w-full h-40 object-cover"
          />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Affordability</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
            Having adequate supply and good transportation options can ease the
            pressure we have on the high cost of living. Keep the building
            concentrated downtown. The current city council has designated 150 W
            to 150 E as higher density, and that's where we should keep the
            density. Let's make it easier for homeowners to add an additional
            dwelling unit at their primary residence.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Trails and Paths -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 flex flex-col items-center">
          <img
            src="/images/EBike.jpg"
            alt="Trails and Paths"
            class="rounded mb-4 w-full h-40 object-cover"
          />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Trails and Paths</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
            We need better connections within Heber and connecting Heber. Let's
            follow the county master trail plan and get those trails built along
            the canals, Center Street, and more. Here is a picture of my ebike
            commute to Deer Valley :) Don't let a little snow stop you!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Latest Blog Posts Section -->
      <section class="mt-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-8 text-center">Latest Updates</h2>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <article class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-4 last:border-b-0">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-1">
                <a
                  href="/blog/2025-07-06-campaign-kickoff"
                  class="text-green-700 hover:underline">Campaign Kickoff</a
                >
              </h3>
              <time class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Sunday, July 6th, 2025</time>
              <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
                I am excited to kick off my campaign for City Council. Thank you
                to all the people who supported me when I ran 2 years ago...
              </p>
            </article>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 text-center">
            <a href="/blog" class="text-green-700 hover:underline font-semibold"
              >View All Posts â†’</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <footer class="bg-green-900 text-white py-4 mt-10 text-center">
      &copy; 2025 Christen Thompson for Heber City Council
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
